text: The Peoples University of Medical and Health Sciences for Women (PUMHSW) () is a public university located in Shaheed Benazirabad District (Nawabshah), Sindh, Pakistan. It was established in 2009. ==External links== * Official website Category:Larkana District Category:Public universities and colleges in Sindh Category:Women's universities and colleges in Pakistan
title: Peoples University of Medical & Health Sciences for Women
